title: Launcher not working after patch 6.11
body:
Hi Guyz, I have had continuous issue with launch button , after patch 6.1 , however deleting Lol launcher and LOL patcher seems to have worked in the past.  
After patch 6.11 The launch button wont work , no matter what I try .  
I have tried to load lol maestro client as well.
A little help would be much appreciated

replies.body:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k9x3QktgWVg

Watch the video brother. It is Turkish but you can understand without any languages.

Tried this fix not working when i click the patcher when im in the files it doesn't work it just crashes again but not with the usual ''pvp patch kernel not working'' but it crashes with bug splat. anyway anyone has any alternative fix?

same with mine, it keeps trying to patch, it takes like a half hour, then it finally gives an error, and the launch button appears, but when i click it, it fades out so it knows i clicked it, but then nothing happens! someone please help us!

Hey there,

Has this issue been resolved for you now?
Mine also like that. Need help..
